═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
USE CASES
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

SCENARIO 1: REVIEWING PROJECT CONVERSATIONS

User wants to review technical discussions in a project without being
distracted by contact requests and handshakes:

1. Open static viewer
